data.description: This beautiful 2115 sq.ft. 3 bedroom and 2 1/2bath has been will maintained. With vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace, skylight in the spacious living area. Kitchen with breakfast and dining area with extra sitting area.  New Refrigerator and washer.  Two bedrooms shared bathroojm 1/2 bath next to kitchen area. Large Master bedroom with bonus are for office, excecise room or den. Dual sinks in master bathroo, sunken tub and show. Walk in closed and moree.  3 car garage with new doors, New perimeter fencing, RV parking. NO HOA but has CCR's.  On the 11th hold on Golf Course, walking distrance to Cararact Lake, close to Forest Land and other amenities. This a must see to appreciate.
